metadata.name: Mirror Mirror#1
metadata.description:
The biggest city in western Japan, Osaka is also well known as the Nation's Kitchen because of the richness of its cuisine. 

This place is the way of getting to know Japan especially on food! The lively atmosphere of shoppers, street food vendors, and tantalizing aromas will make for an unforgettable shopping experience.

I made this piece from a new and unique way of fun, colorful and vibrant.
